<![CDATA[<div><font face="arial">{!Case.Account_Owner_First_Name__c}</font><font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">-</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">We have reached out to {!Case.Account_Owner__c}&nbsp;on several prior occasions to discuss the final direction/approval regarding Entitlement for&nbsp;</font><a href="https://ncr--precert1.cs65.my.salesforce.com/{!Case.AccountId}" style="font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">{!Case.Account}</a><font face="arial">. I have called and left messages, sent emails and scheduled several meetings. I haven’t been able to speak with {!Case.Account_Owner_First_Name__c}. I am needing your assistance to obtain the final direction/approval regarding Entitlements concerns. Here’s a breakdown of the findings:</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">• &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Name of Account - <a href="https://ncr--precert1.cs65.my.salesforce.com/{!Case.AccountId}">{!Case.Account}</a></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">• &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Line of Business -&nbsp;{!Case.Industry__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">• &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Master Customer Number –&nbsp;{!Case.Master_Customer_Number__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">• &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Back Bill $ found –&nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Case.Exception_Back_Bill__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">• &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Future Bill $ Impact –&nbsp;{!Case.Future_Bill_Total__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">• &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Number of Months remaining in Contract –&nbsp;{!Case.Months_Remaining_on_Contract__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">• &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Next billing date –&nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Case.Next_Billing_Date__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">• &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Summary of issues found -&nbsp;</font>{!Case.Description}</div><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1in;"><o:p></o:p></p><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><font face="arial">We are needing to obtain direction on this account. We either need to process the billing or understand why these items aren’t being billed. If you elect not to bill or agree to only a partial bill, we will need to know how this gap in revenue will be made up with the customer. This is necessary since we are required to report each item found and what was done with each.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><font face="arial">&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;">I'd like to schedule a meeting with you </font><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font>on&nbsp;</font>{!Case.Meeting_Date_Time_1__c}</font><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="margin-left: 1in;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><o:p></o:p></font></p><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font>&nbsp;or&nbsp;</font>{!Case.Meeting_Date_Time_2__c}</font><p class="MsoListParagraph" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; margin-left: 1in;"><o:p></o:p></p><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;">. Please let me know which day and time works best for you.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><font face="arial">Thank you for assistance,</font></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial">{!Case.OwnerFullName}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.Title}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!User.Email}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div>]]></td>
